label day2morning:
    
    #test! i added stuff 
    
    scene pink with dissolve
    
    show text "~Day 2~" with pixellate
    
    show text "~Day 2~" with Pause(2)
    
    scene bg room with fade
    
    "You wake up bright and early the next day when your cat is kneading your face."
    l "Ow! Stop it, Momo! I’m awake!" with vpunch
    "Momo" "Meow."
    "You do your usual morning routine, shuffling to the bathroom in a zombie-like fashion. Eventually, you are dressed in your school uniform with ribbons in your hair and a touch of make-up."
    "You look in the mirror and are really feeling the kawaii today. However, you realize that Kaito didn’t show up like he did yesterday morning."
    
    show kaito normal with dissolve
    
    k "Ohayo gozaimasu, Liz-chan! Nothing’s wrong, but uh… "
    
    show kaito worry 
    
    k "Do you have a friend named John?"
    "You can feel your stomach drop and you can’t help but grimace."
    l "Oh gawd… What happened? Did he talk to you?! What did he say?!"
    
    #Maybe have an expression here
    
    k "Nothing! Nothing! He was actually hanging around here before I got here."
    l "REALLY!?"
    k "Yeah… He seems really fond of you!"
    
    show kaito frown
    
    k "He kept talking about how close you two are, how you met, how you laugh at all his jokes..."
    
    show kaito worry
    
    k "...and how you inspired him to get a fedora."
    l "({i}#justneckbeardthings...{/i})"
    
    show kaito frowna
    
    k "He seemed kind of mad at me though…" 
    k "He was also asking what kind of relationship we had and didn’t seem very happy when I said we’d been friends since childhood." 
    k "Said that he was gonna walk you to school today."
    l "Oh my god…"
    
    show kaito laugha
    
    "Kaito laughs lightly. You assume it has something to do with the poorly concealed disgust on your face."
    
    k "I guess it’s good that I told him I usually walk you to school." 
    show kaito worrya
    
    k "He insisted that he wanted to just walk with you, I asked why we couldn’t just walk all together and then he… kind of just ran off?"
    "You sighed with relief."
    l "Thank goodness… Yeah, we’re… kind of friends, but not THAT close. I don’t know, I don’t think he gets it…"
    l "How does he even know where I live?! That’s sooo creepy!"
    k "Hmm… Well, I’m glad I saw him first so I could warn you."
    l "I know, right?! Thank you soooo much for helping me out!"
    
    show kaito smilea
    
    k "It’s no problem…" 
    
    show kaito smileab
    
    k "If you ever need someone to help you or even protect you, just let me know."
    
    show kaito laugh
    
    "He gives you a bright smile highlighted by the morning sunlight. You feel giddy inside."
    l "Thanks… You’re always so reliable.. Kaito-nii-kun!"
    
    show kaito smileb
    
    k "Wow, you haven’t called me that in a long time. I think I still like Kaito-kun more, though. And you’ve always been so good to me, too."
    #        >k "Like yesterday! Thanks so much for helping out."
    l "Aw, it’s nothing. Hehe."
    
    hide kaito
    
    scene bg bluesky
    with fade     
    
    "You two continue on like this as you walk to school together. Maybe it’s just you, but you really enjoyed these little talks you two have together. You’re smiling and jovial the whole time. He seems the same way."
    "You talk about the upcoming festival, the progress, what happened…"
    
    show kaito smilea with dissolve    
    
    k "By the way, feel free to come by our class if you ever want to help. We could always use more people, and it'll be fun."    
    l "I'll see, but since this is the last day before the festival, hopefully they won't be too busy at my own class."
    l "By the way, I can't wait to hear you sing!"
    
    show kaito smileab
    
    k "Eheh, thanks."
    l "Do your classmates even know how amazing your voice is?"
    
    show kaito worrya
    
    k "Not at all, actually… I haven’t sung in front of any of them before."
    l "Really?? But I’ve heard you sing… You haven’t even practiced in front of them?"
    
    #show kaito worryab (Maybe use this?)
    
    k "I haven’t, actually."
    
    show kaito normalb
    
    k "You’re the only one who’s heard me sing before."
    
    "Kaito gives you such an affectionate and trusting smile that your cheeks glow pink..."
    
    show kaito smile
    
    k "Anyway, I'm gonna head to class. See you, Liz-chan!"
    l "Bye!"
    
    hide kaito 
    
    "You try to shoo the hearts away floating over your head as you walk to class."
    
    scene black with dissolve
    
    "That doesn’t last long though because Nick is already there."
    
    scene bg classroom with fade
    show nick serious
    
    "However, his face is sullen and you can see dark circles under his eyes. He is concentrated on scribbling away some notes in his binder."
    l "Good morning Nick-kun~~~!!!"
    n "...Hey."
    l "What’s wrong? You seem tired."
    
    show nick talka

    n "Hmph… it’s nothing. I’m busy."
    l "With what?? Tell me, hey, tell me~"
    
    show nick shock with dissolve
    "Leaning over his desk, you take a peak of what he’s working on."
    
    show nick shockb with dissolve
    "Yep, that’s definitely the homework due today."
    
    show nick defaultb with dissolve
    "You give him an evil smirk. However, he’s already kind of scooted away from you, looking red."
    "Looks like your chest inadvertently invaded his personal space as well." 
    "You can’t tell what he’s more embarrassed about."
    l "Ooooh, you’re a bad student. That’s the English homework due today, huh? Huh!?"
    
    show nick madtb
    
    n "S-shut up! Don’t tell me you already did it!"
    
    hide nick with dissolve
    
    "He quickly shuts his binder as you lean in closer to tease him." 
    "Just as he does, something else flies out of his binder by accident." 
    
    show nick frown with dissolve
    "It’s a letter."
    "Wait, is that YOUR letter?" 
    "You recognize the doodle and hearts you had scribbled on it. That was from over a week ago!"
    l "GASP! Was that my letter to you?"
    
    show nick madtb with vpunch
    n "NO!"
    "Nick quickly swipes it off the ground and shoves it back in his binder."     
    "He hurriedly shoved his binder into his backpack with an irritated look on his face, but refuses to look at you."
    
    show nick madab
    n "It was nothing! B-baka!"
    l "Why are you keeping my letters?? Did you like them that much?"
    n "I told you, they’re not!" with vpunch
    
    show myca normal at left with dissolve
    m "hey gaiz watss happenin" 
    "You turn and see Myca settling in at her desk. She looks short as usual." 
    
    hide nick with dissolve
    show myca normal at center with dissolve
    
    "You quickly rush to her and speak in a poorly concealed hushed voice."
    l "Oh my gosh…! There’s so much I have to tell you…!"
    
    show myca smile
    m "Really? More stuff happened since we talked last night?" 
    show myca normal
    m "And what’s Nick’s problem?"
    l "Apparently, he’s still holding onto the love letter I gave him last week!" 
    
    show myca surprised with dissolve
    
    l "AND! AND!"
    l "John knows where I live!!" 
    l "He was HANGING AROUND my house this morning!"
    m "Uh, don’t break my desk… That’s totally creepy though! How would he have even gotten it!"
    l "I don’t know… I bet he asked around. Maybe he asked my cousin or something." 
    l "Ew!"
    m "Well, did you see him? What’d he do??"
        
    l "Actually, since Kaito is usually there first, he actually ran off!" 
    
    show myca normal
    
    l "Ugh, I’m so thankful Kaito-kun was there!"
    
    show myca smile with dissolve
    
    m "Hah! Did he really just run away like that?" 
    
    show myca giggle with dissolve
    m "Your harem is defending you! Lucky."
    l "H-hey, they’re not my harem!"
    
    show myca normal
    
    m "Speaking of such, what were you saying about Nick?"
    l "Dude, just earlier he accidentally showed that he STILL holds onto the stuff I gave him…"
    
    show myca surprised with vpunch
    m "EhhH!!! USO!!"
    if d1d2_nick:
        m "So not only did he spend all that time with you yesterday and say that weird stuff about not responding to your confession yet…"
    else:
        m "He also kept all your love letters?!"
    m "Who does all that!? He obviously still likes you! It’s even more obvious now!"
    "Before you could damage her desk even more in excitement, you hear the school bell ring." 
    "You rush to your seats as the teacher comes in just on time."

    hide myca with dissolve
    
    "You’re excited to gossip more during lunch, so you have a hard time paying attention during class." 
    "Actually, the more you think about, the more you realize just how close the festival is!"
    "Today would be the last day to work on the preparations…" 
    "Then tomorrow-- tomorrow!-- would be when the festival officially starts." 
    "Do I really have to find a dance partner by then?"
    
    scene bg classroom with fade
    show myca normal with dissolve
    "When the lunch bell rings, you ambush Myca’s desk."
    l "Ahh, I can barely concentrate! Are you serious about this bet thing!?"
    l "Do you really think I have a chance with EITHER of them!?"
    
    show myca smile
    m "Yes and yes! And apparently John knows where you live too!" 
    
    show myca giggle with dissolve
    
    m "Maybe he’s planning the wedding already in his head! Hahaha!"
    l "Don’t say that!! Ughh! And where are you going!?"
    
    show myca normal
    m "Oh, I forgot to mention I gotta go do some last minute Anime Club stuff for lunch. I mean, we’re mostly done but something came up."
    l "Ehhh!? You’re leaving me?!"
    "Myca pats your shoulder."
    
    show myca smile
    m "You’ll be fiiine~ I mean, unless you wanna come with, but uh, I doubt that."
    
    show myca giggle with dissolve
    "You suddenly flash to the last Anime Club meeting where everyone was having pretend ninja fights."
    l "Err… I’ll figure something out."
    m "Okay, bye!"
    
    hide myca with dissolve
    "You stare at your lunch blankly and bite your lip. There’s no way you can eat alone, especially with all these thoughts stressing you out." 
    "You decide to…"
     
